headline: Oil futures up from post-settlement levels as API shows large draw crude supplies
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures inched up from post-settlement levels Tuesday after the American Petroleum Institute showed a much larger draw than expected in U.S. weekly crude supplies.

headline: 3 Large-Cap Stocks with Promising Prospects
summary: Large-cap stocks have the power to shape entire industries thanks to their size and widespread influence. With such vast footprints, however, finding new areas for growth is much harder than for smaller, more agile players.
